<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Set up an <a href="/en/basics/automation/event-procedures">event procedure</a> to automatically send returns to Klarna. For further information about creating returns, refer to the <a href="/en/order-processing/orders/managing-sales-orders#return">Return</a> page of the manual.</p>
